# 🤖 AI Job Match Assistant

> An AI-powered full-stack web application that analyzes your resume against any job description, gives an ATS compatibility score, identifies missing keywords, and rewrites your bullet points — built for freshers applying to software jobs in Germany 🇩🇪

![Project Banner](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Live-brightgreen) ![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11+-blue) ![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-18-61DAFB) ![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-0.111-009688) ![AI](https://img.shields.io/badge/AI-Groq%20LLaMA3-orange) ![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow)

