## 🎯 What This Project Does

Most freshers apply to jobs without knowing if their resume will even pass the ATS (Applicant Tracking System) filter. This tool solves that problem.

You paste a job description from LinkedIn, Indeed, or any company website. You upload your resume as a PDF. The AI reads both, compares them deeply, and gives you:

- **ATS Match Score** out of 100 with explanation
- **5 missing keywords** your resume needs to pass ATS filters
- **3 rewritten bullet points** tailored to match the job description
- **Skills gap analysis** showing what you still need to learn
- **Overall verdict** — Strong Match / Needs Work / Poor Match
- **Recommended job title** to use on your resume
- **Germany-specific tip** for applying in the German job market

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| React 18 | UI framework |
| JavaScript (ES6+) | Logic and API calls |
| CSS3 | Styling and animations |
| Fetch API | HTTP requests to backend |

### Backend
| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Python 3.11 | Core language |
| FastAPI | REST API framework |
| Uvicorn | ASGI server |
| PyPDF2 | Extract text from resume PDF |
| python-dotenv | Load environment variables securely |
| Requests | HTTP calls to Groq AI |

### AI & Deployment
| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Groq API | AI inference engine (free tier) |
| LLaMA 3.3 70B | Large language model for resume analysis |
| Vercel | Frontend hosting (free) |
| Render.com | Backend hosting (free) |
| GitHub | Version control and portfolio |

---

## 🏗️ Project Architecture

```
User Browser
     │
     │  Opens localhost:3000 / vercel URL
     ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│         FRONTEND (React)            │
│                                     │
│  • Shows the form UI                │
│  • Collects job description text    │
│  • Accepts resume PDF upload        │
│  • Displays ATS score + results     │
│  • App.js  App.css  index.js        │
└──────────────────┬──────────────────┘
                   │ POST /analyze
                   │ (FormData: PDF + job text)
                   ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│         BACKEND (FastAPI)           │
│                                     │
│  • Receives PDF + job description   │
│  • Extracts text from PDF           │
│  • Builds AI prompt                 │
│  • Calls Groq LLaMA3 API            │
│  • Parses ATS score from response   │
│  • Returns JSON result              │
│  • main.py                          │
└──────────────────┬──────────────────┘
                   │ POST to Groq API
                   │ (prompt with resume + JD)
                   ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│         GROQ AI (LLaMA 3.3 70B)    │
│                                     │
│  • Reads resume and job description │
│  • Scores ATS compatibility         │
│  • Finds missing keywords           │
│  • Rewrites resume bullets          │
│  • Returns structured analysis      │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

